Sentencas: In this study, the planar anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with straight opening pores were prepared by phase inversion method and the laser ablation technique.
Titulo: Enhanced performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode-supported SOFC with an anode functional layer

Sentencas: The microstructure, thermal expansion behavior, porosity and bending strength of anodes with 3 mol% Y2O3 doped ZrO2 (3YSZ) and 8 mol% Y2O3 doped ZrO2 (8YSZ) were investigated.
Titulo: Enhanced performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode-supported SOFC with an anode functional layer

Sentencas: The bending strength of 144 MPa for NiO-3YSZ planar anode was achieved, which was two times higher than that of NiO-8YSZ substrate.
Titulo: Enhanced performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode-supported SOFC with an anode functional layer

Sentencas: To improve the electrochemical performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode, an anode functional layer of NiO-8YSZ was introduced between NiO-3YSZ anode and electrolyte layer by spin-coating method.
Titulo: Enhanced performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode-supported SOFC with an anode functional layer

Sentencas: The maximum power density of single cell with NiO-3YSZ anode was improved from 365 to 598 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Enhanced performance of NiO-3YSZ planar anode-supported SOFC with an anode functional layer
